                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                        <td>
                            资源说明：所属业务对象为企业：办理过程：1.广东省名牌产品评价中心公布当年开展广东省名牌产品（工业类）评价的产品目录以及相关要求。2.生产评价目录范围内产品、符合条件的企业申请广东省名牌产品（工业类）。3.企业按要求填写申请表格，并报送到市质量技术监督局质量科。4.市质监局组织市有关部门进行初步评议，形成推荐意见，并统一报送广东省名牌差评评价中心。5.广东省名牌产品评价中心组织有关部门和社会团体对企业的申报材料进行初审，并将初审名单及其申请材料分送相应的专业委员会。6.专业委员会按照评价细则对申请产品进行综合评价，形成评价报告，并向广东省名牌产品评价中心提交广东省名牌产品建议。7.广东省名牌产品评价中心将专业委员会提出的建议汇总分析后，提交全体委员会审议确定初选名单，并将初选名单通过新闻媒体向社会公示。8.经过广泛征求意见确定的名单再次提交广东省战略推进委员会全体会议审议、确定并公布。9.授予企业“广东省名牌产品”称号，颁发广东省名牌产品证书及牌匾。

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>

                <script lang="javascript">
                    function limit_go(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='rows']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go3(target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val($("._cur_page", form).val());
                        form.submit();
                    }

                    function limit_go2(e, target) {
                        e = e || window.event;
                        var charcode = typeof e.charCode == 'number' ? e.charCode : e.keyCode;
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");

                        if (charcode != 13) {
                            return;
                        }

                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(target.value);
                        form.submit();
                        if (e.preventDefault) {
                            e.preventDefault();
                        } else {
                            e.returnValue = false;
                        }
                    }

                    function limit_go0(i, target) {
                        var form = $(target).closest("form");
                        $("input[name='page']", form).val(i);
                        form.submit();
                    }
                </script>
